### Auth API (get tokens first!)
### ===========================================

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hello",
  "email": "hello@example.com",
  "password": "password12wwww3"
}

###

### Login (use this to get fresh tokens)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### ===========================================
### Posts API (requires authentication)
### Copy the accessToken from login response and paste below
### ===========================================

@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:3000/post
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "This is my first post!"
}

###

### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:3000/post
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get posts by sender (replace with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/post?sender=USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get post by ID (replace with actual post ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/post/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update post (replace with actual post ID - only owner can update)
PUT http://localhost:3000/post/POST_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Updated post content"
}

###

### Delete post (replace with actual post ID - only owner can delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/post/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

